ZH: 我的屋子很小。
EN: My room is very small.

ZH: 这间屋子很冷。
EN: This room is very cold.

ZH: 她在屋子里唱歌。
EN: She is singing in the room.

ZH: 他把屋子打扫得很干净。
EN: He cleaned the room very well.

ZH: 屋子里有很多书。
EN: There are many books in the room.

ZH: 我的家人都在屋子里。
EN: My family is all in the room.

ZH: 屋子里装饰得很漂亮。
EN: The room is decorated very nicely.

ZH: 这是一间宽敞的屋子。
EN: This is a spacious room.

ZH: 我喜欢在屋子里看电影。
EN: I like watching movies in the room.

ZH: 屋子里的灯坏了。
EN: The light in the room is broken.

ZH: 孩子们正在屋子里玩耍。
EN: The children are playing in the room.

ZH: 我昨晚睡在客厅里，因为屋子里太吵了。
EN: I slept in the living room last night because the room was too noisy.

ZH: 屋子的墙上挂着很多照片。
EN: There are many photos hanging on the walls of the room.

ZH: 屋子里弥漫着烤面包的香味。
EN: The smell of toasted bread fills the room.

ZH: 屋子里有一张舒适的沙发。
EN: There is a comfortable sofa in the room.

ZH: 这座城堡有很多房间和屋子。
EN: This castle has many rooms and chambers.

ZH: 屋子外面下着大雨。
EN: It's raining heavily outside the room.

ZH: 屋子里有一个大书架。
EN: There is a large bookshelf in the room.

ZH: 屋子里都是我的回忆。
EN: The room is filled with my memories.
